import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['age'] = pd.to_datetime(data['age'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='age', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['age'].median(), color='red', label=f'Median: {data["age"].median():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of age?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['height'] = pd.to_numeric(data['height'], errors='coerce')
    sns.boxplot(x=data['height'])
    plt.title('What is the average height of the people in the dataset?', wrap=True)

    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
